the mystery rider is a lost 1928 silent film western action serial directed by robert j. horner and starring william desmond . horner produced and released through universal pictures . afi has the film listed as a &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; feature ( a possible &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; version of the serial ) . a trailer for the film ( or its episodes ) survives in the library of congress .